                    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm text-amber-600 mt-2 space-y-1">
                        <li>Water: ~14.4M people need WASH services; 40% decrease in overall water supply.</li>
                        <li>Agriculture: Olive oil output 105,000 MT (2024/25); Pistachio output 55,000 MT (2024/25). Grain production covers only ~19% of wheat demand.</li>
                        <li>Waste: 80% of solid waste historically went to illegal dumpsites. Vast C&D waste offers recycling potential.</li>
