                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                 <p class="text-xs text-gray-600 mt-1 text-center">This flow aims for zero waste and maximum value from the olive harvest.</p>

                <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-emerald-700 mt-6 mb-3">Powering Sustainable Operations: Energy Solutions</h4>
                <p class="text-stone-700 mb-2">Syria's severe energy crisis, with limited grid availability, poses a significant operational challenge. To ensure consistent production and embody true sustainability, this olive oil facility must prioritize energy independence and efficiency:</p>
                <div class="power-illustration">
                    <div class="power-illustration-row">
                        <span class="power-illustration-icon">‚òÄÔ∏è</span>
                        <p class="text-sm">On-Site Solar PV Generation</p>
                        <span class="flow-arrow text-sm mx-1">+</span>
                        <span class="power-illustration-icon">üîã</span>
                        <p class="text-sm">Battery Storage (BESS)</p>
                    </div>
                     <div class="flow-arrow text-sm my-1">‚¨áÔ∏è</div>
                    <div class="power-illustration-row bg-emerald-100 p-2 rounded">
                        <span class="power-illustration-icon">üè≠</span>
                        <p class="text-sm">Factory Operations (Efficient Equipment)</p>
                    </div>
                     <div class="flow-arrow text-sm my-1">‚ôªÔ∏è</div>
                     <div class="power-illustration-row">
                        <span class="power-illustration-icon">üåø</span>
                         <p class="text-sm">Bioenergy from Pomace (Thermal/Electricity)</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <p class="text-stone-700 mt-2">This integrated approach (Solar PV + BESS + Bioenergy from Pomace + Efficient Machinery) addresses the power challenge, significantly lowers the carbon footprint, and enhances operational resilience and marketability.</p>


                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-3">Illustrative Cost Considerations (Highly Variable in Syrian Context)</h3>
                <p class="text-stone-700 mb-2">The following are typical cost components. Actual figures require detailed on-the-ground feasibility studies in Syria due to extreme volatility and specific local conditions.</p>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-6">
                    <div class="bg-blue-50 p-4 rounded-lg border border-blue-200">
                        <h4 class="font-semibold text-blue-700 mb-2">Indicative CAPEX (Capital Expenditures) Components:</h4>
                        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm text-blue-800 space-y-1 cost-list">
                            <li>Land acquisition/lease and site preparation.</li>
