                 <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-3">Visualizing the Ideal Pistachio Milk Eco-Factory: A Cradle-to-Cradle Cycle</h3>
                <p class="text-stone-700 mb-4">The ideal pistachio milk factory operates on cradle-to-cradle principles, ensuring sustainability at every stage. This diagram illustrates the conceptual flow:</p>
