                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-3">Sandbox Potential & Strategic Fit</h3>
                <p class="text-stone-700">Establishing a model pistachio milk production facility in Syria, integrated with shell valorization, aligns perfectly with the "sandbox" concept. It would demonstrate high-value addition, showcase circular economy principles, create skilled jobs, and potentially attract investment. By focusing on premium quality and unique Syrian origin, pistachio milk can become a flagship product for Syria's eco-friendly industrial sector.</p>
            </section>
        </div>

        <div id="eip" class="tab-content hidden">
            <section class="mb-8 p-6 bg-white rounded-lg shadow">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">The Eco-Industrial Park (EIP) Vision</h2>
                <p class="section-intro">The "sandbox" factory concept is the cornerstone of a larger vision: an Eco-Industrial Park (EIP) in Syria. This EIP would be a collaborative community of businesses working together for enhanced environmental, economic, and social performance. This section explores EIP core principles, lessons from global models, and a phased development approach for Syria, positioning the initial factory as a catalyst for sustainable industrial regeneration.</p>
                
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-3">Core EIP Principles</h3>
                <div id="eipPrinciplesContainer" class="space-y-3 mb-6">
                </div>
                 <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2">These principles define how an EIP functions to create synergistic benefits. Click each for details.</p>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-3">Phased EIP Development in Syria</h3>
                <ol class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-2 text-stone-700">
                    <li><strong>Flagship "Sandbox" Factory:</strong> Establish the first pioneering eco-factory, perfecting its circular processes and proving viability. This factory will meticulously document resource flows and waste streams to inform EIP planning.</li>
                    <li><strong>Attracting Synergistic Industries:</strong> Based on the flagship's outputs/inputs, attract complementary businesses. Develop basic shared infrastructure.</li>
                    <li><strong>Comprehensive Shared Infrastructure:</strong> Invest in common effluent treatment, larger renewable energy installations, logistics hubs, and R&D labs.</li>
                    <li><strong>Full EIP Operation & Governance:</strong> Mature EIP with formal management, facilitating symbiosis, ensuring compliance, and promoting continuous improvement.</li>
                </ol>
                 <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2">A step-by-step approach to building a thriving eco-industrial ecosystem.</p>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-3">Learning from Global EIP Models</h3>
                <div id="globalEipModelsContainer" class="space-y-3">
                </div>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2">Insights from successful international EIPs can inform Syria's approach. Click each model for key takeaways.</p>
            </section>
        </div>

        <div id="strategy" class="tab-content hidden">
