                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Strategic Path Forward: Enabling Eco-Industrial Growth</h2>
                <p class="section-intro">Successfully launching pioneering eco-industries and developing an Eco-Industrial Park in Syria requires a supportive enabling environment. This section outlines key strategic recommendations across policy, infrastructure, finance, skills development, partnerships, and the importance of sustainability certifications. These elements are crucial for attracting investment and ensuring long-term success.</p>
                <div id="recommendationsContainer" class="space-y-2">
                </div>
                 <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2">These recommendations aim to create a fertile ground for sustainable industrial development in Syria. Click each category to explore detailed actions.</p>
            </section>
